{"tid":422514,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Excel 一問","createTime":"2017-10-03T06:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T13:08:53.000Z","uid":86137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3446482220c2564c8559952c8f69e73447ad55b","tid":422514,"uid":86137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"請問有冇高手教我點Del cell入面個&quot;點&quot;. <br />\n冇理由逐個DEL, Crt H 又唔得....<br />\n<br />\nexp: 下面左手邊個點.<br />\n'18/10/2017<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/141947_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F141947_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=0dfe39f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd8b1c040c88d52198a8428ff2b7f94e550234b5","tid":422514,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:23:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"406f0fa446da05e3073ca46b0766d219e8a59131","tid":422514,"uid":86137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Copy落notepad<br />\nreplace完paste返落去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個點其實係引號黎,所以Copy唔到, 你可以試下打."},{"pid":"f694e6ca188d7fd159ce0ebaa63239afdf51cfc7","tid":422514,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:58:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9157ac112d6dbd7915dfe74abb4376755f300e10","tid":422514,"uid":13025,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"資料剖析做到"},{"pid":"5ba302456d03de95c5f8e86f728d1cf2101789a8","tid":422514,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:04:03.000Z","msg":"你唔講都唔知replace唔走"},{"pid":"87eb5d5fdff5d3ebce37c905bb3940fff593aaae","tid":422514,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>資料剖析做到</blockquote><br />\n姐係text to column"},{"pid":"7272d27eb34a7fefb4f2e16be4515aa7b9f291d8","tid":422514,"uid":107881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"copy and paste as value (123) 咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bedf701e2aa398334c69d6c1718f3614a500d92","tid":422514,"uid":61347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"select 曬 all date 嘅儲存格，<br />\n再 資料頁 &gt; 資料剖析 &gt; 步驟3 欄位的資料格式 揀 日期<br />\n完成"},{"pid":"8340db83857fb05bd3037417de6135fb63301a97","tid":422514,"uid":86137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T08:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>copy and paste as value (123) 咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncant copy the dot <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68577be47f85f8a2153b3ce275413854a0f34858","tid":422514,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"係入面加一行column, cell value 打<br />\nFor example 有問題嘅係column A, 開一行column B 第一格打以下一句<br />\n=IF(LEFT($A1,1)=&ldquo;&lsquo;&ldquo;, RIGHT($A1, LEN($A1)), $A1)<br />\n<br />\n之後拉曬佢，再copy 返value 返column A 就得<br />\n<br />\n如果係date 嘅話都可以試下就咁 =DATEVALUE($A1)"},{"pid":"f8f46073d38478b961ecb3fa05b0c626a040d7db","tid":422514,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係入面加一行column, cell value 打<br />\nFor example 有問題嘅係column A, 開一行column B 第一格打以下一句<br />\n=IF(LEFT($A1,1)=&ldquo;&lsquo;&ldquo;, RIGHT($A1, LEN($A1)-1), $A1)<br />\n<br />\n之後拉曬佢，再copy 返value 返column A 就得<br />\n<br />\n如果係date 嘅話都可以試下就咁 =DATEVALUE($A1)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打錯左formula, 改左"},{"pid":"22a81496d9f3efc36bfc895cc44607db2844dc86","tid":422514,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b75ac4c07219c94fad6131601efc1e4d1bf981e2","tid":422514,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10262cb42f591b7799baf57d657fcb24caad4f6a","tid":422514,"uid":107881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"我梗係做到先講出嚟啦傻尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aec99132225d40f8de42eef203db877b4805453","tid":422514,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:41:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"572320b7114258eb7c8e245b24b603bc1bdf480b","tid":422514,"uid":86137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係入面加一行column, cell value 打<br />\nFor example 有問題嘅係column A, 開一行column B 第一格打以下一句<br />\n=IF(LEFT($A1,1)=&ldquo;&lsquo;&ldquo;, RIGHT($A1, LEN($A1)-1), $A1)<br />\n<br />\n之後拉曬佢，再copy 返value 返column A 就得<br />\n<br />\n如果係date 嘅話都可以試下就咁 =DATEVALUE($A1)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打錯左formula, 改左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得左丫, 連登有愛~!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}